_sText:
Well, i got pissed off at seeing these "speedball274724" paintball maps around that look like some kids backyard, so i took 40 minutes of my time to remake the NPPL commander's cup field. (2005) 


 ->  http://nppl.tv/scoreboard/mi05fields/nppl3d.jpg   <-

this is the first real speedball map i have seen.

I highly recommend turning the sniper rifles off since both teams can see each other at spawn. 


Theres 26 spawns, but i don't recommend having 26 players. more like 14-20

YOU CANT FALL OFF THE MAP THE EDGE IS THE SKYBOX!!!
